{"tid":381622,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同女朋友分左手一年","createTime":"2017-08-31T05:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T07:52:47.000Z","uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b804e0303eb267a2f481fb0ac39f321f9caf76dd","tid":381622,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:57:45.000Z","msg":"上年差唔多這個時候同女朋友分手，一開始佢好唔舍得，我地斷斷續續咁來往著，不過最近二，三個月開始慢慢變淡了好多，開始似真係普通朋友咁，我同佢係同公司，但係係好難見到面果種，不過佢最近又掉左黎同我同個辦公室，成日見到她跟其他同事有講有笑，我心裏就會有些難受，見到佢現在好似已經完全唔當我係一回事，記得一開始分手係佢好唔舍得，那時候我好想佢快D無事，無諗過現在到我好唔舍得，我唔想煩到佢，纏住佢之類的，同埋我地肯定無可能再係埋一齊的。有時候睇返以前D相，去返以前成日去的地方，想到佢以後又會有新男朋友，真係好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11ce15f9871270b11fc84dd16964275b9df7465","tid":381622,"uid":123787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"什麼事分手的呢？"},{"pid":"918cd0f4fc154e448e074821483517bc7abad3e4","tid":381622,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:20:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>什麼事分手的呢？</blockquote><br />\n佢同我分手的"},{"pid":"b654f2cf34a8534dd1e07ee0eb44c7cf73010cfe","tid":381622,"uid":10845,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:30:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>什麼事分手的呢？</blockquote><br />\n佢同我分手的</blockquote><br />\n唔舍得您，又同您分手？<br />\n正臭雞"},{"pid":"757b85c9d9995496b00372cfe1bdc2abac7a5269","tid":381622,"uid":41112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:32:23.000Z","msg":"佢有新男朋友關你撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n需要屌醒嗎？"},{"pid":"f846f3f81509d9ce364ba2ee8a97a64dc1e6afe3","tid":381622,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T07:17:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢有新男朋友關你撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n需要屌醒嗎？</blockquote><br />\n見到肯定好傷心，就係知道關我撚事行傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cef475c8e4891516839e41597c0e0c8e80a0f37","tid":381622,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T07:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>什麼事分手的呢？</blockquote><br />\n佢同我分手的</blockquote><br />\n唔舍得您，又同您分手？<br />\n正臭雞</blockquote><br />\n又唔係的，主要我唔好"},{"pid":"246553e98a1172058542570901e7eb8c763f7b00","tid":381622,"uid":139830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T07:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢有新男朋友關你撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n需要屌醒嗎？</blockquote><br />\n見到肯定好傷心，就係知道關我撚事行傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果唔洗見到佢，可能無咩野，現家日日返工對住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b8029d1450aabe8d61346db38186f1404b02a1","tid":381622,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T07:50:35.000Z","msg":"見到佢係到同d同事有講有笑，好想過去屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7bffd19d0b80477ae681ba973a8ae946d25f8c","tid":381622,"uid":122428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:04:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到佢係到同d同事有講有笑，好想過去屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會特登做俾你睇阿"},{"pid":"44cc1674f866a3d485035a28bb576ef8b7bf1157","tid":381622,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:51:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見到佢係到同d同事有講有笑，好想過去屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會特登做俾你睇阿</blockquote><br />\n唔係了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6536dfe674117ae11c2dc243e3c1dd3e7b6c45e3","tid":381622,"uid":122428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見到佢係到同d同事有講有笑，好想過去屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會特登做俾你睇阿</blockquote><br />\n唔係了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你又知<br />\n女人一定小心眼過男人"},{"pid":"0aa5f352ae70c1a4dd652623ae4bbc17ccf50db1","tid":381622,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:06:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見到佢係到同d同事有講有笑，好想過去屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會特登做俾你睇阿</blockquote><br />\n唔係了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你又知<br />\n女人一定小心眼過男人</blockquote><br />\n有時想等埋佢一齊坐車，佢都唔多想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416ffee72b1ab332d746faf4f7b2cd8015f50a95","tid":381622,"uid":11082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:08:07.000Z","msg":"仲叫女朋友"},{"pid":"3d9d580608c64e426263a25a3534e4abcb3668c3","tid":381622,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:08:11.000Z","msg":"分手時，我對佢好好，雖然係佢話分手，過左段時間就咩都變曬了"},{"pid":"b05889517b4a996fe013d4fa9c75d6ec5d7027e0","tid":381622,"uid":130342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:10:36.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n<br />\n利申:我都係"},{"pid":"eb297ba7f05bbf2c3ec9be7f77931cafafe5e60f","tid":381622,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:17:19.000Z","msg":"岩岩等左佢一陣，想話一齊走，但係見到佢都唔多想，我就自己走了，之後係電話屌鳩左佢幾句，佢成日問我，究竟想點，問我都分左手重想佢點對我，但係見到佢果種好想同你保持距離果種態度，真係好撚嬲，岩岩分手時，果時我重成日陪佢，怕佢唔開心，現家內左了，就好似無左件事，其實我唔係想要求D咩，只係想就算係朋友，理論上也是好好果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875ce9b8be9a3c1e2b4c5130a6d8bdb7753d9957","tid":381622,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:30:11.000Z","msg":"果時同佢分手，情況有些特別，我地講好左就係我們相識果日分手，果日我地好早就出左黎，因為之前兩年我地都把果日當係記念日咁慶祝，我買左隻手表送比佢，佢買左條蛇送比我（我好鍾意養爬蟲果D野），之後同佢坐左係太平洋大半日，重用電話係到睇斧山行，之後夜黑就去左食壽司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我以為分手後會一路路都好好，岩岩分手時，我覺得成個人都好自由，無諗過過左之後，現在先開始傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf8704735a4bbc4c3759c7640076286ef48d6f6","tid":381622,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:31:51.000Z","msg":"現家"},{"pid":"2f05791c976a950de8fa96dbee87f42e9e9e982f","tid":381622,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:33:17.000Z","msg":"你講到岩岩分手時仲咁sweet咁個陣叫做分手咩？"},{"pid":"086ebb11481fb9d230ad744469fe9ca79df9d63a","tid":381622,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:35:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講到岩岩分手時仲咁sweet咁個陣叫做分手咩？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都唔知，唉"},{"pid":"bd8e9d7302fe5f7f2684186d3301a61df2353d34","tid":381622,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你講到岩岩分手時仲咁sweet咁個陣叫做分手咩？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都唔知，唉</blockquote><br />\n我以為分左，都重會好好，不過內左，就慢慢淡了，佢話佢都要識男朋友，結婚生仔的"},{"pid":"cb204b8fb9dc7ba4f05ac786fc01d9b805610671","tid":381622,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:37:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩等左佢一陣，想話一齊走，但係見到佢都唔多想，我就自己走了，之後係電話屌鳩左佢幾句，佢成日問我，究竟想點，問我都分左手重想佢點對我，但係見到佢果種好想同你保持距離果種態度，真係好撚嬲，岩岩分手時，果時我重成日陪佢，怕佢唔開心，現家內左了，就好似無左件事，其實我唔係想要求D咩，只係想就算係朋友，理論上也是好好果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做乜係電話屌鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊個陣都成日燥底？"},{"pid":"4cc2af6cdc9bff994391c8a236e44ef879870291","tid":381622,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩等左佢一陣，想話一齊走，但係見到佢都唔多想，我就自己走了，之後係電話屌鳩左佢幾句，佢成日問我，究竟想點，問我都分左手重想佢點對我，但係見到佢果種好想同你保持距離果種態度，真係好撚嬲，岩岩分手時，果時我重成日陪佢，怕佢唔開心，現家內左了，就好似無左件事，其實我唔係想要求D咩，只係想就算係朋友，理論上也是好好果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做乜係電話屌鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊個陣都成日燥底？</blockquote><br />\n唔係呀，係鬧交時先會，佢本身都係煩膠黎，脾氣都幾差下，所以岩岩都比佢屌返我轉頭"},{"pid":"bad555ef3654c9bbc268e85ef1190be63bee04cd","tid":381622,"uid":40994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:49:14.000Z","msg":"之前一齊左幾耐先分手？"}]}